        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer176879949" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6089207239057578423">Another amazing book from Iris Murdoch. She managed once more to bring up some questions about types of behaviour in this life, in a very londonese-like spirit, gently uncovering mysteries of human nature. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

